panels.text:
You are Jarv. {pool:jarvMoods:0}

Fifty visits. The archive has a dedicated wing now.

{pool:jarvIntros:1}

Three years ago, the Grand Dominion shattered.

In the Crystal Spire, the shatter was documented in real time. The Archivist filed it under 'catastrophic events, external, category: significant.'

{pool:priorRunSummaries:0}

And yet — {pool:priorRunOpenings:0}

You push the feeling aside. The Spire is waiting.

It has always been waiting. It files everything.
